    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/d7b71f2450e3a6ce107d9367e3693381.poster.avif?t=1700585765\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/d7b71f2450e3a6ce107d9367e3693381.webm?t=1700585765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/d7b71f2450e3a6ce107d9367e3693381.mp4?t=1700585765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Kayak League:</strong> Rocket-powered kayaks, stylized courses, and easy-to-learn, hard-to-master gameplay. Compete, socialize, and customize your loadout in vibrant environments.<br><br>With singleplayer time-trials and 20+ player tournaments consisting of multiple elimination rounds, in various game modes like first-to-finish, demolition arena and crystal collection.<br><br>It's a mix of Fall Guys, Rocket League and Mario Kart. Dive into the excitement of racing and casual mini-games with friends.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/82bb7aa443b0983756af09f554bb5d69.webp?t=1700585765\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br>Maneuvering your kayak is easy to learn, yet very hard to master. Train your paddle proficiency in offline mode, solo/party online mode or in custom lobbies. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/69e0c5f57ef4a32ddf2d45166efdf870.poster.avif?t=1700585765\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/69e0c5f57ef4a32ddf2d45166efdf870.webm?t=1700585765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/69e0c5f57ef4a32ddf2d45166efdf870.mp4?t=1700585765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/19fa0ecdaa963115869fc046bd05dd54.webp?t=1700585765\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br>Unlock kayaks, suits, hats, accessories, paddles and companions. Equip, store or trade your collected items.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/d1b6fc8a643c4b5c5fcc531ed9aa22fa.poster.avif?t=1700585765\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/d1b6fc8a643c4b5c5fcc531ed9aa22fa.webm?t=1700585765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/d1b6fc8a643c4b5c5fcc531ed9aa22fa.mp4?t=1700585765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/150a734ffabead97d10d61be9dd367ba.webp?t=1700585765\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br>Encounter and master an ever-increasing number of obstacles, from moving walls to lava faucets.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/aad167f50a5323e7001190526777c468.poster.avif?t=1700585765\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/aad167f50a5323e7001190526777c468.webm?t=1700585765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2207960/extras/aad167f5